Catch Me if You Can;;89;;96;;PG-13;;Frank Abagnale, Jr. (Leonardo DiCaprio) worked as a doctor, a lawyer, and as a co-pilot for a major airline -- all before his 18th birthday. A master of deception, he was also a brilliant forger, whose skill gave him his first real claim to fame: At the age of 17, Frank Abagnale, Jr. became the most successful bank robber in the history of the U.S. FBI Agent Carl Hanratty (Tom Hanks) makes it his prime mission to capture Frank and bring him to justice, but Frank is always one step ahead of him.;;Crime,Comedy,Drama;;Steven Spielberg;;2002;;Leonardo DiCaprio,Tom Hanks,Christopher Walken,Martin Sheen,Nathalie Baye,Amy Adams,James Brolin,Brian Howe,Frank John Hughes,Steve Eastin,Chris Ellis;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/catch_me_if_you_can